sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Candidato autenticado
  participant FE as Front /jobs/cv
  participant BFF as back-bluee
  participant TAL as talent (RMQ)
  participant USR as users/auth (RMQ)
  participant DB as MongoDB

  C->>FE: GET /jobs/cv
  FE->>BFF: GET /auth/jobs/me
  BFF->>USR: RMQ auth.me
  USR->>DB: get user by id
  USR-->>BFF: user + tenantId + roles
  FE->>BFF: GET /job-applications?tenantId=<tenantId>
  BFF->>TAL: RMQ job-applications.get
  TAL->>DB: get config (sections/fields)
  TAL-->>BFF: configuración CV
  BFF-->>FE: config + user.cvData
  FE-->>C: render dinámico con HeroUI (Input/Select/Checkbox)

  C->>FE: Guardar CV
  FE->>BFF: PUT /auth/jobs/profile { cvData }
  BFF->>USR: RMQ auth.update-candidate-profile
  USR->>DB: update user.cvData
  USR-->>BFF: user actualizado
  BFF-->>FE: ok

